thread.title: Paige, Xavier Woods Will Not Face Action from WWE over Leaked Videos, Photos
thread.title_full: Paige, Xavier Woods Will Not Face Action from WWE over Leaked Videos, Photos

author: Joseph Zucker
title: Paige, Xavier Woods Will Not Face Action from WWE over Leaked Videos, Photos
text: Paige, Xavier Woods Will Not Face Action from WWE over Leaked Videos, Photos Ian Gavan/Getty Images Joseph Zucker Featured Columnist March 21, 2017 WWE won't punish Xavier Woods and Paige for the time being after explicit videos and photos of the two leaked online over the weekend, Wrestling Observer Radio 's Dave Meltzer reported Tuesday (h/t Wrestling Inc's Marc Middleton ). Meltzer said the two stars could face repercussions should a sponsor or a prominent figure voice concerns about the incident to WWE. More to follow.
